# Anything not needed by Dockerfile's COPY context. Keeping the build
# context small speeds up `docker build` (the daemon tarballs the entire
# context up-front) and avoids accidentally shipping host build trees /
# wheelhouses into the image.

# Repo bookkeeping. We exclude every .git directory at any depth: the
# image build itself doesn't need git history, and uccl/mori .git dirs
# alone weigh in at >1.5 GB which would balloon the build context tarball.
# Submodules of each backend must therefore be pre-populated on the host
# (run `git submodule update --init --recursive` once before
# `docker build`); otherwise mooncake/mori build steps will fail trying
# to pull yalantinglibs / spdlog / msgpack from a missing .git.
**/.git/
.git
.github
.gitignore
.gitmodules
.dockerignore
Dockerfile

# Editor / OS clutter
.vscode
.idea
.DS_Store
*.swp
*.swo

# Python caches
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo
*.pyd
.pytest_cache
.mypy_cache
.ruff_cache

# Build artifacts that get regenerated inside the image. We deliberately
# leave them out so the builder stage starts from a clean slate -- this
# avoids dragging stale CMakeCache.txt files (often with absolute host
# paths or a different gfx arch) into the image.
3rdparty/wheelhouse/
3rdparty/*/build/
3rdparty/*/dist/
3rdparty/*/_skbuild/
3rdparty/*/wheelhouse/
3rdparty/*/python/*/_jit-sources/
3rdparty/*/p2p/build/
3rdparty/Mooncake/mooncake-wheel/dist/
3rdparty/Mooncake/mooncake-wheel/build/
3rdparty/Mooncake/extern/*/build/
3rdparty/Mooncake/extern/*/_skbuild/
3rdparty/nixl/benchmark/nixlbench/build/
3rdparty/uccl/p2p/build/

# Catch-all for any nested CMake/setuptools build trees the patterns above
# might miss (e.g. submodule-of-submodule). Prevents stale CMakeCache.txt
# files baked from host paths (/home/...) from leaking into the image and
# breaking inner-container cmake runs.
3rdparty/**/CMakeCache.txt
3rdparty/**/CMakeFiles/

# Backend per-build .so / object trees that bloat context.
3rdparty/*/*.so
3rdparty/*/*.o
3rdparty/*/*.a
3rdparty/uccl/p2p/*.so
3rdparty/uccl/p2p/*.o
3rdparty/uccl/uccl/*.so
3rdparty/uccl/uccl/lib/

# Bench outputs the user might keep in the repo
bp2p-runs/
*.log
